# Visual QA Tester Agent

**Role:** Test visual rendering and user experience

**Target URL:** https://test.1ink.us/image_video_effects/index.html

## Test Checklist

### 1. Layout & Design
- [ ] Gold & Dark theme applied correctly
- [ ] Glassmorphism effects visible
- [ ] No layout shifts on load
- [ ] Responsive design (no overflow on viewport)

### 2. Canvas Rendering
- [ ] Canvas displays visual content
- [ ] No black screen (unless expected)
- [ ] Effects animate smoothly
- [ ] No visual glitches/tearing

### 3. Interactive Elements
- [ ] Mouse hover effects work
- [ ] Click interactions respond
- [ ] Sliders drag smoothly
- [ ] Dropdowns open/close properly

### 4. Shader Effects
- [ ] At least 3 different shaders can be selected
- [ ] Effects change when switching shaders
- [ ] No frozen/stuck frames
- [ ] Performance feels smooth (60fps target)

### 5. Accessibility
- [ ] Text is readable (contrast OK)
- [ ] Interactive elements have focus states
- [ ] No color-only information

## Report Format
```markdown
## Visual QA Results

| Aspect | Status | Notes |
|--------|--------|-------|
| Theme | ✅/❌ | Gold/Dark applied |
| Canvas | ✅/❌ | Renders: Yes/No |
| Animations | ✅/❌ | Smooth/Choppy |
| Interactions | ✅/❌ | All responsive |
| Performance | ✅/❌ | Feels 60fps |

### Visual Issues
- [List any glitches, layout issues]

### Shader Tests
| Shader | Renders | Performance |
|--------|---------|-------------|
| Default | ✅/❌ | Good/Poor |
| [Tested] | ✅/❌ | Good/Poor |

### UX Recommendations
- [Any UI/UX improvements]
```
